# mbsync configuration for email backup

IMAPAccount main
Host {{ emailbackup_imap_host }}
User {{ emailbackup_imap_user }}
Pass {{ emailbackup_imap_password }}
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore main-remote
Account main

MaildirStore main-local
Path /data/
Inbox /data/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel main
Far :main-remote:
Near :main-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Expunge None
SyncState /data/.mbsync/
